$NetBSD: patch-configure,v 1.2 2022/04/05 09:24:29 adam Exp $

Sun audio support.

Enable PIC and section_data_rel_ro on NetBSD, even on i386,
to avoid text relocations.

Fix install_name_dir on Darwin.

Do not use 'rsync'.

